{"tid":291091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"平治狂飆14公里撞3車　13警車圍捕拘司機","createTime":"2017-06-20T09:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T15:27:02.000Z","uid":48093,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a68d49d29b4d1f094cc1ee55e99d3342656edd5e","tid":291091,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:35:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170620/photo/bkn-20170620172140453-0620_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170620173122\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170620%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170620172140453-0620_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170620173122&h=5b1ec60b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170620/photo/bkn-20170620172140453-0620_00822_001_02p.jpg?20170620173122\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170620%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170620172140453-0620_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20170620173122&h=03006f23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下午4時許，警方新界南總區交通部人員在葵涌青葵公路發現一輛可疑平治房車，惟示意其駛往路邊協助調查時，該車司機未有理會，反而踩油加速逃走，警員遂通知上峰增援，並驅車尾隨窮追，雙方爆發追逐戰，該平治狂飆逾14公里，至沙田正街沙田廣場對開時，因交通擠塞被迫收油，期間司機企圖「捐車罅」突圍而出，惟因通道過於狹窄，他連環撞毀最少3輛私家車後，最終突圍失敗停下。<br />\n<br />\n未幾，逾13輛警車趕至現場，將平治房車重重包圍，並將涉事南亞裔司機拘捕，警方現時封鎖現場調查。"},{"pid":"958e3f7667238f6b119f4a6cf1b83282fd054b73","tid":291091,"uid":42767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://orig04.deviantart.net/e132/f/2013/328/d/3/gta_v__wanted_3_stars_by_lunicaura106-d6vjfj0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forig04.deviantart.net%2Fe132%2Ff%2F2013%2F328%2Fd%2F3%2Fgta_v__wanted_3_stars_by_lunicaura106-d6vjfj0.png&h=d3011e5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"827c3d52afd2238b77642291ac24c6aaf38147f5","tid":291091,"uid":8934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:37:38.000Z","msg":"蝻"},{"pid":"c35059b34901a07615e96ac81edde219b3bfdbb1","tid":291091,"uid":14103,"lik